# textdomain: mcl_barrels
Barrel=Sod
Inventory=Inventar
27 inventory slots=27 mest v inventarju
Barrels are containers which provide 27 inventory slots.=Sodi so vsebniki, ki nudijo 27 mest v inventarju.
To access its inventory, rightclick it. When broken, the items will drop out.=Za dostop do inventarja kliknite nanj z desno tipko. Če sod razbijete, bodo predmeti padli ven.
Barrel Open=Odprt sod